{"tid":1656011,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"區選提名 - 要搵手足幫手","createTime":"2019-10-15T10:59:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-16T12:42:07.000Z","uid":334450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c77c6733a2063ffbbc3b80a1a4b030bdab676b90","tid":1656011,"uid":334450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T10:59:36.000Z","msg":"最近附近朋友度見到淨係得1個鄧家彪出選，唔想俾佢自動當選呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以同朋友想出選試下。嗰區係沙田水泉墺邨，而家唔夠提名，差幾個，有無手足可以幫下手???<br />\n<br />\n嗰區勁多新移民、廢老，不過無登記做選民<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n手足今晚幫手盡力推推，怕唔夠時間。<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9a251bc89ab5e8eeacc1b1fd009cf5407360e24","tid":1656011,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T11:56:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">觀塘手足麻煩認住呢個女人！<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OwW9jJU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOwW9jJU.png&h=73f2a385&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2BZiXv5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2BZiXv5.png&h=a6c82315&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/16TLCwj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F16TLCwj.png&h=fa2d6f61&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dhCAfin.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdhCAfin.png&h=50c1e7a9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bfz3pbV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fbfz3pbV.png&h=8